# seokit docs

Public API is two Playwright matchers:

- `toHaveMetadata`
- `toHaveJsonLd`

Document them in `apps/docs/content/docs/matchers.mdx`.

Each matcher extracts an actual value and deep-partial compares to `expected` (strings may be `RegExp`).

## Do not

- Reintroduce a public rule registry / per-rule MDX pages
- Add response/robots.txt/sitemap matchers unless explicitly requested (use Playwright for HTTP)
- Add Open Graph / Twitter as first-class matchers unless explicitly requested
